          "date": "2026-04-22 02:04:04.000000000",
          "tz": -240
        },
        "subject": "LU-20178 tests: add compression test suite",
        "message": "LU-20178 tests: add compression test suite\n\nAdd sanity-compr.sh test suite for CSDC with 19 test cases\ncovering:\n\n- Basic write/read with each compression algorithm\n  (lz4, lz4hc, lzo) and all supported chunk sizes\n- Compression ratio validation ensuring compressed data\n  is smaller than uncompressed for compressible content\n- Incompressible data handling (random data)\n- Mixed I/O patterns: sequential, strided, append\n- Edge cases: partial chunks, exact chunk boundaries,\n  files smaller than one chunk\n- Multi-component layouts with compression on selected\n  components\n- Integration with existing Lustre features: OST pools,\n  striping configurations\n- Stress tests: concurrent compression from multiple\n  clients\n\nSigned-off-by: Brian Barbisch <brbarbis@microsoft.com>\nTest-Parameters: Ignore\nChange-Id: Id5b518554cccd0a605de4821ff6f335e49a1912b\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
